Remove silence and divide utterances:
remove_silence_libri.sh
remove_silence_gsc.sh

Acoustic feature extraction:
We use Numpy 2d-array whose first dimension is time and second one is acoustic feature's dimension.
When extracting MFCC feature, the first dimension is ignored because it conveys only energy.

gsc_preprocess.py: make acoustic features from Google Speech Commands.
remsil_gsc_preprocess.py: make acoustic features from silence removed Google Speech Commands.
librispeech_preprocess.py: For LibriSpeech.
remsil_librispeech_preprocess.py: For silence removed LibriSpeech.


